-d6YU4KPKjTplShZhxLPIUg">Vũ Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%ADnh/T%E1%BA%A3o-nh%E1%BA%A1n/poem-zLV6cqjVw2CdUO5mTPOh5g">Tảo nhạn - 早雁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%ADnh/author-xRP1RhUO6M2EVstuQOukRA">Cao Bính</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%C3%B4-t%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BB%81/poem-bR8QGem88oZhdNps2IvS6Q">Tặng Tô tứ Hề - 贈蘇四徯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Thanh-Kh%C3%A2u-t%E1%BB%AD-ca/poem-1cDYBHKHiWXC3r_OhZMuig">Thanh Khâu tử ca - 青丘子歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-CZQp1s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/%C6%AF-Huy%E1%BB%81n-V%C5%A9-pha-t%C3%A1c/poem-6j0eRkgz9qmB3I_cEHxVFw">Ư Huyền Vũ pha tác - 於玄武陂作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br></div>	</div>
